        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/cdc98d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-30T22:23:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Not surprising she likes them too. Robert Parker was a pretty darn big fan too. He gave 6 different wines 100 points since 2011 and gave another 6 bottlings 99 points. Not too shabby\u2026</p>",
