        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/arv_r/{size}/76949_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-31T01:15:38.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I looked at the 2015 No. Rhones scores/notes, and a cursory look at K&amp;L suggested many have already been cleaned out.  Still a few left though.</p>\n<p>Not flashy, but I\u2019d like to pick up some of the large production Crozes in this vintage.  As Joe Cz notes, the ripeness/quality extended down the line this year.</p>",
