        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Arv R\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Arv R:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I looked at the 2015 No. Rhones scores/notes, and a cursory look at K&amp;L suggested many have already been cleaned out.  Still a few left though.</p>\n<p>Not flashy, but I\u2019d like to pick up some of the large production Crozes in this vintage.  As Joe Cz notes, the ripeness/quality extended down the line this year.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Think that\u2019s a good move. Got a couple of cases of Graillot myself.</p>",
